The American Historical
Magazine, and The American Lawyer.

00:01:15.780 --> 00:01:21.270
He has won two journalism awards
and has two books to his credit:

00:01:21.270 --> 00:01:25.990
The Recollections of Margaret
Cabell Brown Loughborough,

00:01:25.990 --> 00:01:29.190 position:56%
